author: Socrates
message: The greatest way to live with honour in this world is to be what we pretend to be.
title: Thought of the day

author: Henri Bergson
message: To exist is to change, to change is to mature, to mature is to go on creating oneself endlessly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Albert Einstein
message: Try not to become a man of success but rather try to become a man of value.
title: Thought of the day

author: Byron Pulsifer
message: You can't create in a vacuum. Life gives you the material and dreams can propel new beginnings.
title: Thought of the day
